The impact of social determinants of health on acute kidney injury
                    Samira Bell 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0001-9100-15751, Rolando Claure-Del Granado 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0002-8163-37792,3, Nuttha Lumlertgul4, Mignon McCulloch 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0003-2876-47855, Amira Mohamed6, Neesh Pannu7, Manisha Sahay 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0001-5534-25168, Danielle E. Soranno 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0001-7019-809X9, Marlies Ostermann 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0001-9500-908010, Ravindra Mehta 
